response.overview: The German football club EINTRACHT FRANKFURT is set to celebrate its 120th anniversary in the Commerzbank Arena (stadium) in the most extraordinary and unprecedented settings on Saturday, June 29th, 2019. Together with the hr-Sinfonieorchester and many other artists, the club is set to embark on a unique journey back through time, and through their history. There will be musical highs and lows, in the style of the "moody diva". Also, the thrash metal legends TANKARD will perform the club’s anthem 'Schwarz-weiß wie Schnee' together with the Sinphony-Orchestra, for the first time.
response.title: 120 years of Eintracht Frankfurt
